Class CrimeRecord

java.lang.Object
seng202.group2.model.CrimeRecord
public class CrimeRecord
extends java.lang.Object
CrimeRecord stores the categorical data associated with a record of a crime. TODO: Implement validity checking when setting attributes that should follow a format, or whose domain is a proper subset of its type, such as fbiCode.
